node.text:
I don’t know 🤷🏿‍♂️, how you’re going to absorb this message, but please I need y’all to understand : I won’t be doing any bodybuilding competition throughout the year 2020. I need some time to bring up my size and muscle density .
.
.

I’m sorry to everyone who really wanted me to compete again next year. This decision was made by myself and my mum , after I Placed 4th twice 🎖🎖this year.
.
.
.
I’m still grateful to God , my mum , @bodymoney , @ifesfitworld , @naziftm16 and @ruff_diesel  for your support and motivation. God bless you all abundantly. Amen 🙏🏿. Till 2021 it’s OFFICIAL GROWTH OFF SEASON.

node.text:
Alot of sensitive people have understood that I am now posting just old pictures 😂, don’t be offended, my physique and personality is under construction now. 

I hope everyone is enjoying themselves, I will be training triceps and shoulders today … what’s on your schedule today ? 

#doublepanda #fitness #bodybuilding #workout #physique #nigeria #ghana #melanin #lagos #london #instagood

node.text:
NEW WEEK , SAME GOALS , SAME HUNT !!!

🙏🏾 Dear God, don’t allow my hard work be in vain, put me in the path to always be grateful. 

These lonely days will soon be over 😁🙏🏾.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 🅲🅰🅻🅴🅱  🌀 in Nigeria with @amlsnnational, @medical_laboratory_scientists, @medicallaboratoryscientist, @_medlab_, and @medicallaboratoryscientistshub. May be an image of 3 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text:
😁 You better be nice to me , because I might be the lab scientist who will either collect your blood sample tomorrow or run analysis on your body fluid . 
With that been said please don’t be expecting health or medical content from my page 😂. Being a bodybuilder and crypto business man is enough content already. 

What do you guys think should I be dropping health & medical content or not ? 

Enjoy your weekend and don’t forget to trade your coins with me 👨🏾‍💻🤌🏾💯💸. 

#sunday #medicallaboratoryscience #scientist #crytocurrency #bodybuilder #nigeria #ghana #southafrica #london
